Today, I learn about the CSS ( Inline, Internal, External).
Also , get to know about the Selector (Element, Id, Class, Group ).
Learn about the RGB color , rgba , HSL, hsla and the Hexadecimal Color.
Get to know about the font size ( in px, em , rem, vw, vh, % ).
Also, learn about the Font family ( font-family: "Gillsans","serif" .
Also, Font-weight, Font-Style.
Another Shortcut method for it : By using the Font Shorthand Way (i.e., h{ font-style:Italic; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; font-family: Georgia,serif; }  ).
